{"tid":378862,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一段 拍拖最難忘回憶","createTime":"2017-08-28T19:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T18:16:09.000Z","uid":80740,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"79602114ff08f81237edc87e67bdba87c9ff6e66","tid":378862,"uid":80740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T19:43:40.000Z","msg":"第一次想拖初戀女朋友隻手，<br />\n果陣中學雞既我咩都唔識，<br />\n上網學埋曬d屎橋，話想送樣禮物比佢叫佢攤開手～～<br />\n然後就一下拖左落去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果段路成程好怕羞，仲要拖得唔係好舒服<br />\n最後拖到出曬手汗咁問：不如鬆開下咯，有d熱呀<br />\n佢話：好呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家有無好純真 諗返起又有少少關家姐既拍拖史分享下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e5c92fccf071be83f6682366407b20b7f221e7","tid":378862,"uid":4550,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T19:44:38.000Z","msg":"破處"},{"pid":"da8b78de987b00a339b57045f77024c52877e85c","tid":378862,"uid":73729,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T19:45:38.000Z","msg":"左手拖右手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fbc02f3a3577f142ad8ab438a53aad3122784d1","tid":378862,"uid":80740,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T19:45:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>破處</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n肯定好爽"},{"pid":"2cb47f873d4cce486000625bac278a806a4bf154","tid":378862,"uid":80740,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T19:48:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>左手拖右手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中間仲有條巨龍"},{"pid":"7d00c116212a1348842651d859deef609d421a44","tid":378862,"uid":80740,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T19:51:21.